  "description": "<p>A strong and light expedition shelter to handle the most severe conditions. The Bastion's dome structure sheds wind and provides ample living space for up to 4 people. Reinforcements on the fly and high-strength guylines stand up to Denali-like storms, while the two vestibules offer practical space for all your gear.</p><ul><li>Sturdy yet lightweight silnylon fly has long-lasting polyurethane coating for waterproofness</li><li>Floor is fully-taped nylon with 10,000mm polyurethane waterproof coating</li><li>DAC aluminum poles have pressfit connectors for high strength-to-weight</li><li>Pole sleeves and clips resist snow loading and are easy to set up in cold conditions</li><li>Polyurethane front window is rated to -51C</li><li>Fly vents and closable mesh panels balance ventilation and weather protection</li><li>10 interior pockets and hanger points keep you organized</li><li>Heavy duty reflective guylines and glow-in-the-dark zipper pulls for easy of use in the dark</li><li>Includes 4 snow stakes</li></ul>",
